---
// Services V2 — 4 formats d'intervention
---

<section id="services" class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4" style="color: var(--accent);">Mes services</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Quatre formats d'intervention,<br />
        <span class="font-serif italic" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">du diagnostic à la mise en œuvre.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Service 1 — Conseil stratégique -->
      <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-3xl card-hover" style="background: var(--bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="text-xs font-medium" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">À partir de</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold">500 € HT / jour</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Conseil stratégique</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Sparring partner sur vos enjeux digitaux et IA. Vision long terme, priorisation des chantiers, alignement business / data / exécution.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Roadmap projet priorisée</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Alignement équipes métier et techniques</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Suivi mensuel ou retainer</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 2 — Atelier diagnostic -->
      <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-3xl card-hover" style="background: var(--bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="text-xs font-medium" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">À partir de</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold">1 500 € HT</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Atelier diagnostic IA</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Une journée d'atelier structuré avec votre équipe pour identifier les cas d'usage IA à plus forte valeur et bâtir un plan d'action concret.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Décomposition de la problématique</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Construction du workflow cible</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Livrable : rapport + roadmap</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 3 — Formation -->
      <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-3xl card-hover" style="background: var(--bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-purple-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/20">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="text-xs font-medium" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">À partir de</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold">1 500 € HT / jour</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Formation</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Sessions adaptées aux dirigeants et aux équipes. Initiation IA, cadrage de projets IA, marketing digital. Finançable OPCO / CPF.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Format inter ou intra-entreprise</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Cas pratiques sur vos enjeux</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Montée en autonomie de vos équipes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 4 — Accompagnement -->
      <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-3xl card-hover" style="background: var(--bg-secondary); border: 1px solid var(--border);">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-emerald-500/20">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-right">
            <div class="text-xs font-medium" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">Sur devis</div>
            <div class="text-lg font-bold">Forfait projet</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Accompagnement à la mise en œuvre</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">Pilotage de votre projet IA, de la conception à la mise en production. Coordination avec partenaires techniques pour la partie développement.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Gestion de projet de bout en bout</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Réseau de partenaires devs et no-code</li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Mesure d'impact et KPI</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
